  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Volmoed is a retreat and conference centre in Hermanus, South Africa. The focus of its mission for the past 34 years is reconciliation, focused on racial reconciliation, and reconciliation within families or groups. Groups or individuals come for training programs, conferences on reconciliation, group learnings, wellness retreats, peace &amp; to relax. Due to Covid-19, there are no visitors and no income. They are meanwhile raising funds to keep Volmoed going.</narrative>
  </description>
